<p><b>Railroad Retirement Board (RRB) Covina, California District Office</b></p>

<p>The RRB administers retirement benefits for most current, former, and retired railroad employees, including spousal benefits, and survivor benefits for families of deceased employees who are insured under the Railroad Retirement Act. Eighty District Offices assist individuals in resolving claims under the Act.</p>

